reviews.reviewText: This is not what I expected. The description says it's made of alloy, which I expected to be some sort of metal, but it's entirely plastic except for the crystals.I do think they have a cute look in the car, but I'm not sure how well they work yet because they didn't come with any pads to put essential oils on. I was aware there was no sample of oil, which is fine because I have my own, but how am I supposed to use this if it doesn't have a cotton pad? This just leaves a bad taste in my mouth and no scent in the air. I wouldn't order these again.
